  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_unread_message" data-step-uuid="22e2c90a-251b-475c-91d7-67b17a5c0d24">
    <h2 id="view_unread_message" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Unread Message</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/142/257/original/8ef8cbd3-360d-49c4-90b9-4de2dd0371e5.png" srcset="" alt="View Unread Message" height="431" width="399">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_D62F5A10-22F5-0135-6ED3-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>All unread messages have an indicator next to the message. Once a Conversation has been read, the blue dot changes to a gray circle.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="mark_as_unread" data-step-uuid="49452d44-8611-4f0a-9e70-ab7c54acca5d">
    <h2 id="mark_as_unread" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Mark as Unread</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/157/814/original/e5fb9064-315e-4d9a-a4fc-495308712652.png" srcset="" alt="Mark as Unread" height="305" width="377">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_D62F8F90-22F5-0135-6ED5-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you want to mark a conversation as unread, click the read indicator [1]. The message will now show the unread indicator [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="mark_multiple_messages" data-step-uuid="026a65ad-3dba-4049-8065-44a70137cbfd">
    <h3 id="mark_multiple_messages" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Mark Multiple Messages</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/639/193/original/0de530bb-e371-44d4-930a-d0f104e3cc02.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/639/193/medium/0de530bb-e371-44d4-930a-d0f104e3cc02.png" srcset="" alt="Mark Multiple Messages" height="744" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_D62FBDE0-22F5-0135-6ED7-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can mark multiple conversations as unread or read by pressing the command key (Mac) or the control key (Windows) while clicking multiple messages, or by selecting the message checkbox [1]. </p>
<p>Click the <strong>More Options</strong> icon [2] and select the <strong>Mark all as unread </strong>link [3]. </p>
<p>To mark unread conversations as read, select the <strong>Mark all as read</strong> link [4].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

